      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.0.2": "进程可以分叉，在一个区块中等待，并在后续区块恢复，而不必重新启动本地执行上下文。",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.1.0": "交互",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.1.1": "元组空间 + COMM",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.1.2": "等待中的取用（Consume）与另一笔交易的写入（Produce）相匹配；匹配会唤醒后续执行，而无关工作继续推进。",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.2.0": "授权",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.2.1": "OCAP 权限边界",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.2.2": "不可伪造的能力引用被显式传递，让每一步只获得所需权限；身份不会自动把无关权限带入当前环境。",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.3.0": "重放",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.3.1": "ReplayTrie",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.3.2": "只记录真正影响结果的非确定性 COMM 选择，使验证者能够复现同一段执行。",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.4.0": "结算",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.4.1": "BlockGit + Block Merge",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.items.4.2": "并发工作进入经过验证的 Fringe；相互重叠的结果会在最终确认前被判定为接受、拒绝或待定。",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.text": "长时间运行的服务之所以保持一致，是因为每一步都能执行、交互、携带显式权限、进行确定性重放，并沿一条可验证的原子路径<span class=\"no-break\">完成结算</span>。",
      "parallelConcurrentComposable.foundations.title": "是什么让一项服务<span class=\"no-break\">持续运行</span>",
